    "From all the proposed models, the MULT ALL model creates the most meaningful clusters.",
    "Except Problem, all clusters for semantically related classes are well identifiable in Fig. 11c.",
    "Although MULT GRP performs best, the clusters are not consistent in Fig. 11b.",
